text: (shai t n thveu dau che neah) daembi komaoy puokke korp sakkar champoh a l laoh del chea anak leatatradeang nouv avei del leak touk leumekh chea chraen chean ning phendei( ampi tukaphlieng roukkhcheate ning avei phe sa ng tiet) haey trong doeng nouv avei del puok anak leakbang ning avei del puok anak leat tradeang
